parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, leading to accidents. It can also result in loss of control over climate control, audio, and navigation systems, which can be inconvenient and potentially dangerous.
symptoms: The infotainment system freezes
locks up
or restarts randomly
causing loss of control over climate control
audio
and navigation systems. The system may also display error messages or fail to display important warnings
such as the "check entire surroundings" warning when using the rearview camera.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning backup camera can increase the risk of accidents or injuries when reversing, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The backup camera fails to initialize
displays a black or white screen
or takes an excessively long time to load. The system may also fail to display gridlines and warning messages
making it difficult to judge distances and avoid obstacles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The powertrain and electrical system failures can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle's powertrain and electrical systems fail
causing the vehicle to stall or lose power. The failure can also cause the gauges and lights to malfunction or reset
making it difficult to monitor the vehicle's performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunctioning advanced safety features can increase the risk of accidents or injuries, especially when driving at high speeds.
symptoms: The advanced safety features
such as intelligent cruise control and collision avoidance systems
malfunction
causing the vehicle to brake abruptly or fail to respond to obstacles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the OCS can lead to the airbag system malfunctioning, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The passenger airbag sensor light remains on or flashes
indicating that the system is not functioning properly
even when an adult is seated in the passenger seat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the traction control system can cause loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The traction control system does not function when needed
and there are no warnings on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The airbags fail to deploy in the event of a crash
or the airbag warning light remains illuminated.
